des:
Your FESH app is your solid starting point for optimal utilization of the many opportunities you find with the TUYA platform. Use the FESH app in English with Alexa Skill for voice control and enjoy the smart comfort the FESH products give you.
After connecting Alexa to your FESH products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "FESH" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "FESH" app;
(3). You need to have some FESH devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "FESH" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "FESH SIMPLY SMARTER!" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "FESH SIMPLY SMARTER!" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "FESH SIMPLY SMARTER!", and you'll be navigated to "FESH SIMPLY SMARTER!" login page;
(9). Open “FESH“ App, click More Service, choose “Alexa”. Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on plug.”
“Alexa, turn off plug.”
